******
[2] China: avian influenza human (Guangdong) H7N9
Date: Tues 27 Jan 2015
Source: Avian Flu Diary [edited]
http://afludiary.blogspot.com/2015/01/guangdong-province-reports-2-more-h7n9_27.html


The Health and Family Planning Commission of Guangdong Province reported on 27 Jan 2015 2 cases of avian influenza H7N9 in Shenzhen and Meizhou City.

Case 1. Female, 75 years old, with history of hypertension, currently residing in Longhua District, was diagnosed on 26 Jan 2015 with avian flu H7N9. She is in critical condition, in Shenzhen hospital.

Case 2. Female, 62 years old, with history of hypertension, now living Meijiang District, was diagnosed on 26 Jan 2015 with avian flu H7N9. She is in critical condition, in Meizhou City, admitted as an inpatient to the hospital.

[Byline: Michael Coston]

